data.description: Check out the virtual tour! Located in the beautiful Miramesa, this charming two story home features 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths & a home office. Enjoy the open floorplan, high ceilings, a spacious open living area, & covered patio in the backyard. /2 Car Garage home features Kitchen w/ 36'' Designer Cabinets, Beautiful kitchen with white cabinets. Granite Countertops, Breakfast Bar and Stainless Steel Appliance Pkg! Dining Room, Game Room & Study. Master Suite with Relaxing Tub & Separate Shower, Dual Sinks & Large Walk-In Closet! All Bedrooms Have Walk-in Closets! Extensive 20" Tile Floors; 2'' Faux Wood Blinds; Covered Rear Patio; Irrigation System; Energy Efficient 16 SEER HVAC System & MORE! *Other upgrades may be present in home. Miramesa is conveniently located with easy access to Grand Parkway & minutes from the Towne Lake Boardwalk where you can enjoy shopping & dining. This home will not last!
